{"tid":573941,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"做緊老人院 你問我答","createTime":"2018-02-27T02:52:18.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-27T11:25:30.000Z","uid":126651,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"887a44ea96cec49d9ea9f19b12bf54a981ef0d76","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:52:18.000Z","msg":"做緊老人院一年鬆d<br />\n有做過津院&amp;私院<br />\n做過真落手照顧老人家的護理員<br />\n即係餵飯沖涼執屎尿<br />\n有乜想問？<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 如有雷同，實屬發夢<br />\n注意 : 不相認<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e123e674ecbef303c832b07a7f47c9d8a6ea8b69","tid":573941,"uid":157349,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T02:56:02.000Z","msg":"其實有無認真幫老人家沖涼 <br />\n老人家瀨屎尿有無出手打過佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"696c7393cf170d15d16585c1f8e0ce1f1b26ac66","tid":573941,"uid":33982,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:03:24.000Z","msg":"有冇諗住考保健員"},{"pid":"44e478657f348f546cbfad73becd61466d415cc4","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:07:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實有無認真幫老人家沖涼 <br />\n老人家瀨屎尿有無出手打過佢地 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係特別要求嘅通常隔日沖一次涼<br />\n啲罅位會特別沖乾淨啲<br />\n應該咁講..<br />\n你見到嘅地方就會好乾淨<br />\n<br />\n瀨屎尿就正常嘅<br />\n不過十個有九個都有包尿片<br />\n一日痾幾次屎都唔會出手(冇咁衰<br />\n最多鬧兩句<br />\n但伸手入去玩屎就gg啦<br />\n啲姐姐會好大力咁幫佢地抹手<br />\n但通常都唔會整損佢哋<br />\n因為家屬好麻煩<br />\n<br />\n利申 : 我未試過虐待老人家，我做唔出違背自己良心嘅事"},{"pid":"867e420d0de7fa9b12baec1b3a3274cdcaacde2b","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:07:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有冇諗住考保健員</blockquote><br />\n考左啦"},{"pid":"cf4d92259e9d792471a2608beb152cde4080c70a","tid":573941,"uid":39274,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:08:20.000Z","msg":"我都做緊HW 津院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d46742b997f8ff491f5da0b553e1ed8d3580eead","tid":573941,"uid":10325,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:08:52.000Z","msg":"點樣忍d臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a2ca2e57425c250afb042c237e15f9752fdcda1b","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:09:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都做緊HW 津院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n而家現職私院<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e61bfe7d7e8150fca1e0d9f5e59a706fef01ea99","tid":573941,"uid":168506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:10:32.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"62c4fec4c7d84e677f54781edd1733261b358335","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:10:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>點樣忍d臭味<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實我都唔知點解我會忍受到啲味<br />\n戴口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 其實都冇乜用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"061a17a545c5f4ed17e32a355ce6895205ba4ad4","tid":573941,"uid":23833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:11:52.000Z","msg":"新仔幾錢個月<br />\n<br />\n你又幾錢？"},{"pid":"57a858d75ba4d6c3a12be387c8658cc729d9c9e0","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:12:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有咩難忘經歷</blockquote><br />\n冇乜嘢真係好特別難忘<br />\n你想聽開心定唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2d6eb73db8cee3e4cc823febc26543b3081a7366","tid":573941,"uid":168506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:13:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"fac508f388419c7248de454014c8af99e32f8ab5","tid":573941,"uid":45442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:13:55.000Z","msg":"環境&amp;服務，自己係個度做覺得點？<br />\n如果叫你放自己屋企人入去住你放唔放心？<br />\n宿位價錢幾多？<br />\n<br />\n最近有屋企人有需要入hostel<br />\n但咁多間都唔知點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無行內出名伏既千祈唔好入？"},{"pid":"d5679568feca642045073c5c356ab3a391f0fb61","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:15:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>新仔幾錢個月<br />\n<br />\n你又幾錢？</blockquote><br />\n睇吓你做咩位<br />\npcw 13k起 11hr 6day<br />\nhw 14k起 9hr 6day"},{"pid":"e0dfe9b76c402205050bb39258eca147ca2ed93c","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:19:28.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩難忘經歷</blockquote><br />\n冇乜嘢真係好特別難忘<br />\n你想聽開心定唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>兩樣都分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞笑先<br />\n有日有個阿婆醫院要佢驗大便<br />\n我哋叫佢屙屎嗰陣同我地講聲(佢醒醒地嘅<br />\n點知轉個頭佢用紙巾包住舊屎<br />\n拎去前台叫姑娘拎去驗<br />\n<br />\n唔開心<br />\n我諗最難忘係第一次要面對你照顧左好耐嘅婆婆走咗"},{"pid":"620cb5877e3333bc283069fd556ef636c5e9b658","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:23:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>環境&amp;服務，自己係個度做覺得點？<br />\n如果叫你放自己屋企人入去住你放唔放心？<br />\n宿位價錢幾多？<br />\n<br />\n最近有屋企人有需要入hostel<br />\n但咁多間都唔知點揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有無行內出名伏既千祈唔好入？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n老人院真係一分錢一分貨<br />\n睇吓你要乜嘢服務<br />\n甲一院個d肯定貴13k@月，但有保證<br />\n劍X、X橋 嗰啲出晒名唔得嫁啦<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我做咗呢行一個禮拜嗰陣應承過自己<br />\n無論發生乜嘢事<br />\n我都唔會比我屋企人住老人院<br />\n唔係我覺得d老人院唔好<br />\n而係我有能力做到<br />\n點解要交比第二個人隻手做"},{"pid":"ce73c53ffb7d85998ec0459f83a2397f013ab359","tid":573941,"uid":168506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:28:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9dbea3bce3f686d7117d9a5bbc48920fb7f23dd8","tid":573941,"uid":126651,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:35:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>有咩難忘經歷</blockquote><br />\n冇乜嘢真係好特別難忘<br />\n你想聽開心定唔開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>兩樣都分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搞笑先<br />\n有日有個阿婆醫院要佢驗大便<br />\n我哋叫佢屙屎嗰陣同我地講聲(佢醒醒地嘅<br />\n點知轉個頭佢用紙巾包住舊屎<br />\n拎去前台叫姑娘拎去驗<br />\n<br />\n唔開心<br />\n我諗最難忘係第一次要面對你照顧左好耐嘅婆婆走咗</blockquote>仲識用紙巾包住比你地算唔錯<br />\n有認知障礙隨時徒手比你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n都幾sad 應該成日面對生離死別<br />\n通常係訓到唔識醒定點</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n所以我米話佢醒醒地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n訓到唔識醒就少d<br />\n見佢唔對路就會即刻call車<br />\n通常唔習慣為多<br />\n例如有啲老人家見到你都會嗌聲你姐姐仔<br />\n佢走咗之後<br />\n你會覺得成間院靜左<br />\n會好唔習慣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eca373034763ad8be8b28f22e916e0a96cb339ae","tid":573941,"uid":62760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"政府嗰啲好似幾好"},{"pid":"ddedce51a1ee95eab5db751e09c65606dac57fdd","tid":573941,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:42:09.000Z","msg":"你覺得津院定私院好做"},{"pid":"42abd009bc4750d2b7c1b94207fc6d7d748c83ef","tid":573941,"uid":48623,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"eca373034763ad8be8b28f22e916e0a96cb339ae","tid":573941,"uid":62760,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:39:50.000Z","msg":"政府嗰啲好似幾好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T03:42:25.000Z","msg":"排到個孫個孫再出世都未有位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"840c385166ec1ed6e7e84de1ab8729e55e913da9","tid":573941,"uid":24227,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":